@Flybubble and @windcast.weather have teamed up

Flybubble Weather. Shows 2 day summary and detailed
site forecasts along with a clear green light when your
chosen locations are flyable.

Total value nearly £200, including the Windcast
weather cube!

is:
Tag 3 fellow paraglider pilots
Ensure you both follow @Flybubble and
@windcast.weather

Share it to your story
